OL,3,CNew operator announced to run Bradford
OL,4,CLive
OL,6,FA new operator has been announced to
OL,7,Frun the new Bradford Live music venue
OL,8,Fafter a "challenging" 12 months that
OL,9,Fsaw the original operators pull out.
OL,11,FTrafalgar Entertainment, which runs 21
OL,12,Fvenues across the world, including the
OL,13,FOlympia Theatre in London and the
OL,14,FTheatre Royal Sydney in Australia,
OL,15,Fwill now take on the city centre venue.
OL,17,FThe #50m venue which was formerly an
OL,18,FOdeon cinema and Gaumont before that,
OL,19,Fwas due to open as a live music venue
OL,20,Fin November.
