OL,3,CNew operator announced to run Bradford
OL,4,CLive
OL,6,FHowever, in a shock announcement in
OL,7,FSeptember, operators NEC pulled out of
OL,8,Fthe venue, saying it would be "better
OL,9,Fserved by an alternative operator."
OL,11,FThe decision left Bradford Council
OL,12,Fsearching for a new operator for what
OL,13,Fis seen as the biggest regeneration
OL,14,Fscheme in the city centre.
OL,16,FOn Monday, 17 February, the council
OL,17,Fannounced that after a competitive
OL,18,Ftender process, global live
OL,19,Fentertainment company Trafalgar
OL,20,FEntertainment had been named as the
OL,21,Fnew operator.
