OL,3,CNew operator announced to run Bradford
OL,4,CLive
OL,6,FSir Howard Panter, co-founder of the
OL,7,Fcompany, said their immediate priority
OL,8,Fwas "supporting and promoting Bradford
OL,9,Fas the UK City of Culture 2025."
OL,11,FIt is expected that the venue will be
OL,12,Fopen by autumn, and Trafalgar has also
OL,13,Fbeen in discussion with Bradford
OL,14,FCulture Company to agree how the venue
OL,15,Fcan play a role in Bradford's UK City
OL,16,Fof Culture programme this year.
OL,18,FThe venue will have capacity for 3,000
OL,19,Fpeople seated or 3,500 people standing
OL,20,Fin the main auditorium as well as
OL,21,Fother event spaces.
