OL,4,CLive
OL,6,FThe former Odeon Cinema was originally
OL,7,Fbuilt in 1930s but the building has
OL,8,Fstood empty since the cinema closed in
OL,9,F2000.
OL,11,FTrafalgar's ambitious plans for the
OL,12,Fvenue include full use of all the
OL,13,Frestored and reimagined spaces, to
OL,14,Finclude conferences, exhibitions,
OL,15,Fevents, weddings, graduations and
OL,16,Fbanqueting events.
