OL,3,CNew operator announced to run Bradford
OL,4,CLive
OL,6,FCllr Susan Hinchcliffe, Leader of
OL,7,FBradford Council said: "I am delighted
OL,8,Fto be able to make this announcement
OL,9,Fand welcome Trafalgar Entertainment to
OL,10,FBradford.
OL,12,F"After the challenges of the last 12
OL,13,Fmonths, we can now look forward to
OL,14,Fseeing this iconic part of Bradford's
OL,15,Fhistory open and playing a big part in
OL,16,FBradford's future.
OL,18,F"The venue will be fully open in
OL,19,FAutumn this year, and playing a part
OL,20,Fin our UK City of Culture celebrations
OL,21,Fprior to that as promised."
